snippet.title: Judge Gets ANNOYED That Amber Heard Keeps Telling Fake Stories in Court
snippet.description:
►Judge Gets ANNOYED That Amber Heard Keeps Telling Fake Stories in Court
In 2011, Depp and Heard met while filming "The Rum Diary," a film based on a Hunter S. Thompson novel. They married in February 2015, but Heard filed for divorce just over a year later, alleging Depp of striking her and obtaining a temporary restraining order against him.
